               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> In going through the fair there were a lot of people round a gambling table, which drew my attention—I saw the gentleman put his hand into his pocket, and in drawing it out he let the gloves fall to the ground—I picked them up, but before I could return them I was taken by the officer.</p>
